Type: Package
Package: LikertMakeR
Title: Synthesise and Correlate Likert Scale and Rating-Scale Data Based
    on Summary Statistics
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hume", "Winzar", , "winzar@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7475-2641"))
Description: Generate and correlate synthetic Likert and rating-scale data
    with predefined means, standard deviations, Cronbach's Alpha,
    Factor Loading table, and other summary statistics.
    Worked examples and documentation are available in the package vignettes,
    accessible via browseVignettes("LikertMakeR").
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/WinzarH/LikertMakeR, https://winzarh.github.io/LikertMakeR/
BugReports: https://github.com/WinzarH/LikertMakeR/issues
